STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Saint H. MERILAN a/k/a, Saint Hilaire Merilan, Saint H. Merialn, Saint Merilan, Jason Williams, Defendant-Petitioner. C-217 Sept. Term 2017
079388 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 20, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002826-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
